  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7401972/" class="title-link">有关蒙元水军与蒙宋战争一节</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7401972"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/freyteamo/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1453488-178.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/freyteamo/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">sub rosa</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-03-09"
      class="main-meta">2015-03-09 22:14:42</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7401972_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  萧老师在文中梳理了蒙元水军发展历程，最紧要的是水军在蒙宋战争中发挥的关键性作用。不同于认为蒙元是以骑兵夺得天下的大众的一般印象，能够战胜倚江淮天堑、江海水军俱发达的宋，关键的部分还是投降来的宋军将领带来的水军战略知识。有关长江沿线决战的部分相当精彩。  唯有...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7401972/#comments">(7回应)</a>
